  <brief_title>Hydroxychloroquine in Treating Patients With Newly Diagnosed Chronic Graft-Versus-Host Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase III Trial of Hydroxychloroquine + Standard Therapy for Chronic Graft-Versus-Host Disease</official_title>
